{"tid":2155792,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特朗普抱怨洗頭難，美國政府提議加快淋浴出水速度","createTime":"2020-08-14T04:27:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T09:26:41.000Z","uid":53062,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"3e0be009fb92df1bfd59897ee80fbe80b30347dc","tid":2155792,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T04:27:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-53774640\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-53774640&d=Bi55TGPCxKeiDoZ%2FBZgBR79ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=3778054e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-53774640&h=e5e7a5de\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-53774640</a><br />\n<br />\n「你打開淋浴，如果你和我一樣，就沒法好好洗你的秀髮，」特朗普本月在位於俄亥俄州的惠而浦公司（Whirlpool Corporation）一家製造廠參觀時說。<br />\n<br />\n根據美國老布什（George H.W. Bush）政府1992年簽署的一項法律，美國淋浴噴頭（花灑）設備每分鐘的出水量不得超過2.5加侖（約9.5升）。<br />\n<br />\n2011年，奧巴馬（Barack Obama）政府認定，有多個淋浴噴頭的產品也必須符合這一總量限制。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普政府希望能將這一限制放寬至每個噴頭，而不是整個固定裝置。<br />\n<br />\n「所以這些淋浴噴頭，在你洗澡時沒水了。你想洗手，也沒水了。那你要怎麼辦？你只能多站一會還是多洗一會澡？我不知道你的，但我的頭髮一定要完美。保持完美，」他說。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"992104567cf3cd2d568fda4f623c22116051c0c0","tid":2155792,"uid":53062,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T04:29:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/7dVifY0PgKc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7dVifY0PgKc&d=Bi55TGPCxKeiDoZ%2FBZgBR79ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=cf6a5fb2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7dVifY0PgKc</a><br />\n<br />\nMy hair has to be perfect <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24bde8f55a6c118d98a2d00750370a7640975fc5","tid":2155792,"uid":197761,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T04:31:33.000Z","msg":"<img src